"{\"uid\": \"financialpost.com-pmn-business-pmn-olympic-track-uniforms-spark-online-debate-about-who-designed-them-and-why-theyre-so-skimpy\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Author of the article:  You can save this article by registering for freehere.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 78, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orsign-inif you have an account.\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - U.S. track and field athletes have around four dozen pieces to choose from when assembling their uniforms at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 120, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999745341, \"rank\": 2.5284045037138288e-11, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one grabbing the most attention is a high-cut leotard that barely covers the bikini line and has triggered debate between those who think it is sexist and others who argue they do not need the internet to make sure they have good uniforms.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe now to read the latest news in your city and across Canada.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999998562734721, \"rank\": 1.4303121877983118e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe now to read the latest news in your city and across Canada.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999998562734721, \"rank\": 1.4303121877983118e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\",