http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abigail_Irozuru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abigail_Irozuru\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Answer: Yes.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get the latest headlines, breaking news and columns.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up you consent to receive the above newsletter from Postmedia Network Inc.  A welcome email is on its way.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia Network Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not see it, please check your junk folder.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next issue of Top Stories will soon be in your inbox.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We encountered an issue signing you up.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please try again  Interested in more newsletters?Browse here.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Track and Field said uniform maker Nike consulted with several athletes while designing the uniforms, which were unveiled in Paris earlier this week.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999893702808, \"rank\": 6.639943412850799e-09, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8551118026529555, \"rank\": 0.16943760992258902, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999454303, \"rank\": 5.476726408044575e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among those taking part in the rollout were world champion sprinter Sha'Carri Richardson and Olympic gold medalist Athing Mu, who wore versions of the uniform that covered more than the kit that grabbed so much attention.\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nike responded to a request for comment from The Associated Press by sending a statement quoting executive John Hoke as saying the company worked \\\"directly with athletes throughout every stage of the design process.\\\"\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8551118026529555, \"rank\": 0.16943760992258902, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 1879, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9335683699522509, \"rank\": 0.07115882691194934, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.978058559651503, \"rank\": 0.015444015444015344, \"text\": \"Hoke\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"USATF seconded that, saying \\\"athlete options and choices were the driving force for USATF in the planning process with Nike.\\\"\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Track_&_Field\", \"score\": 0.9993189960469652, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USATF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Track_&_Field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Track_&_Field\"}, {\"begin\": 2167, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8551118026529555, \"rank\": 0.16943760992258902, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Katie Moon, the defending Olympic champion in the pole vault who is sponsored by Nike, offered the most impassioned defense of the company on social media.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1019281313411637e-14, \"text\": \"Moon\", \"types\": [\"Q634\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\"}, {\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8551118026529555, \"rank\": 0.16943760992258902, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She began her post by saying the leotard shown on the mannequin \\\"was concerning, and warranted the response it received.\\\"\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she said the women had at least 20 different combinations of uniforms to compete in, and can also choose the styles made for men.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you attack the buns and crop top saying something along the lines of it's 'sexist' (which if that was our only choice, it would be), even if it's with the best of intentions, you are ultimately attacking our decision as women to wear it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nike previously found itself at the center of another uniform debate.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2845, \"end\": 2849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8551118026529555, \"rank\": 0.16943760992258902, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several Major League Baseball players complained about the fit of the new Nike Vapor Premier during spring training.\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2923, \"end\": 2944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball\", \"score\": 0.9997055384500247, \"rank\": 0.00015152491437552286, \"text\": \"Major League Baseball\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Baseball\"}, {\"begin\": 2989, \"end\": 2993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8551